Package org.eclipse.equinox.p2.core

Class ProvisionException

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Throwable
java.lang.Exception
org.eclipse.core.runtime.CoreException
org.eclipse.equinox.p2.core.ProvisionException
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ProvisionException extends CoreException
A checked exception indicating a recoverable error occurred while provisioning. The status provides a further description of the problem.
Since:
2.0
See Also:
  • Serialized Form
Restriction:
This class is not intended to be subclassed by clients.
